with a stockbroker.

00:11.370 --> 00:16.001
My mom is dating a yogi
who only eats raw. [thud]

00:16.010 --> 00:18.308
Thomas, you better
be in that bed.

00:18.310 --> 00:20.005
I will tell mom.

00:20.020 --> 00:22.614
I think
my brother is up.

00:22.620 --> 00:24.145
[thud]

00:24.150 --> 00:26.744
Damn it, thomas.

00:29.620 --> 00:31.156
That's weird.

00:31.160 --> 00:32.252
What?

00:32.259 --> 00:33.455
I heard something.

00:33.460 --> 00:36.498
What is it?

00:36.500 --> 00:38.423
Maybe it's
your stalker.

00:38.430 --> 00:39.829
No one believes me.

00:39.840 --> 00:41.968
I swear someone has
been following me around.

00:41.970 --> 00:44.268
They were lurking in
the back yard last week.

00:44.270 --> 00:45.806
You don't
have a stalker.

00:45.810 --> 00:47.505
Famous people have
stalkers.

00:47.510 --> 00:49.239
You have a creeper
with a crush.

00:49.250 --> 00:52.049
That qualifies
as a stalker.

00:52.050 --> 00:53.074
Chill out, hannah.

00:53.080 --> 00:55.048
Don't flatter yourself.

00:55.050 --> 00:57.417
[footsteps]

00:57.420 --> 01:00.185
What's going on?

01:00.190 --> 01:03.979
I heard something.
Don't hang up.

01:03.990 --> 01:06.425
Ok. I'm here.

01:19.010 --> 01:21.274
Talk to me, hannah.

01:22.480 --> 01:25.848
Hannah, you're
scaring me.

01:25.850 --> 01:27.272
Hannah?

01:27.280 --> 01:27.940
Shh!

01:27.950 --> 01:29.748
Hannah, what's
going on?

01:29.750 --> 01:32.617
I don't know.

01:35.490 --> 01:38.687
Hannah, what's
going on?

01:38.690 --> 01:40.749
The door is open.

01:40.760 --> 01:42.956
Are you serious?

01:43.670 --> 01:46.162
Do you see anything?

01:53.780 --> 01:56.374
[deadbolt clicks]

01:56.380 --> 01:57.779
[sighs]

01:57.780 --> 02:00.647
[creak]

02:00.650 --> 02:02.675
I think someone
is in the house.

02:02.690 --> 02:04.169
Oh, my god,
get out of there.

02:04.190 --> 02:06.215
I can't. I can't
leave without thomas.

02:06.220 --> 02:08.449
If anything happens,
call 911.

02:08.460 --> 02:11.327
[panting]

02:11.990 --> 02:14.459
Thomas? Thomas?

02:14.460 --> 02:16.349
Thomas, where are you?

02:16.370 --> 02:19.192
What are you doing,
trying to scare me to death?

02:19.200 --> 02:23.262
There's someone
in the house.

02:23.270 --> 02:25.568
Girl: Talk to me.
What's happening? Hannah?

02:25.570 --> 02:26.708
I'm calling
the police.

02:26.710 --> 02:29.031
Yes, yes. Call the police.
I don't know what to do.

02:29.040 --> 02:31.270
Get out of the house,
hannah, now!

02:31.280 --> 02:33.806
Get out of the house!

02:33.820 --> 02:35.015
Aah! Aah!

02:35.020 --> 02:37.148
Oh, my god,
he's in the house!

02:37.150 --> 02:40.916
[both screaming]

02:41.560 --> 02:44.655
Help! Help! Help!

02:44.660 --> 02:47.652
Somebody help us!

02:47.660 --> 02:50.789
Help!

03:39.010 --> 03:42.310
