to go further,

03:47.060 --> 03:47.845
But it was late,

03:47.860 --> 03:49.817
And I had to open up
this morning.

03:49.830 --> 03:51.252
You gonna
see him again?

03:51.260 --> 03:54.184
No. He was nice, but
there was no chemistry.

03:54.200 --> 03:56.999
But you had fun.

03:57.000 --> 03:58.468
How'd you sleep?

03:58.470 --> 04:00.962
