he will never hurt you again.

04:06.880 --> 04:08.530
I know.

04:08.540 --> 04:11.305
Look. Keep dating.
Keep it light.

04:11.310 --> 04:14.769
Have fun.
Have crazy sex.

04:14.780 --> 04:15.747
Crazy sex?
Yeah. Yeah.

04:15.750 --> 04:17.309
Who are you having
crazy sex with?

04:17.320 --> 04:19.209
Ho ho ho!
Do as I say, not as I do.

04:19.220 --> 04:20.483
Seriously, I've
known you 3 years.

04:20.490 --> 04:22.754
Unless you're keeping
them all a secret--

04:22.760 --> 04:23.909
[cell phone rings]

04:23.930 --> 04:26.024
