know how to do that?

04:26.030 --> 04:27.429
It's freaky.

04:27.430 --> 04:29.398
Ha ha! Hello.

04:29.400 --> 04:31.266
Yeah. Tell him
I'll call him back.

04:31.270 --> 04:33.295
Thanks. I'm out.

04:33.300 --> 04:35.940
It's on the house.
Call me later.

04:35.940 --> 04:37.863
I'm here all night.

04:37.870 --> 04:40.840
Remember, have fun.

04:48.920 --> 04:52.709
