at [LA.X. And confirm

05:40.540 --> 05:42.463
They closed the file on
the September threat.

05:42.470 --> 05:44.029
Let's put it to bed.

05:44.040 --> 05:45.405
Morning.
Coffee?

05:45.410 --> 05:47.970
Hey, jack.
I'm good.

05:47.980 --> 05:49.300
How about you, um--

05:49.310 --> 05:50.937
Belle.
No, thank you.

05:50.950 --> 05:52.770
I'm good.
You sure?

05:52.780 --> 05:54.077
I'm good.

05:54.080 --> 05:55.479
Weiss called to follow up
on the lopez case.

05:55.480 --> 05:57.869
Erotomania, guy who was
obsessed with the soap star--

05:57.890 --> 06:00.450
Jack: Morning.
I brought coffee.

06:00.460 --> 06:04.886
I went all ILA. With nonfat,
nondairy quad shot lattes.

06:04.890 --> 06:06.153
Did I get close?

06:06.160 --> 06:07.855
Oh, well,
thank you.

06:07.860 --> 06:10.056
Jack, don't
buy me coffee.

06:10.070 --> 06:11.629
Seriously? You're gonna
get mad at coffee?

06:11.630 --> 06:13.667
I'm just trying to make
a good impression,

06:13.670 --> 06:14.592
My ongoing struggle.

06:14.600 --> 06:15.795
You want to make
a good impression?

06:15.800 --> 06:18.167
