in the unit

06:35.290 --> 06:36.280
And an assistant--
belle.

06:36.290 --> 06:38.122
What about all the
other people? Various.

06:38.130 --> 06:40.326
There's vice, domestic
violence, mental health.

06:40.330 --> 06:42.628
People get moved around
a lot, and space is tight.

06:42.630 --> 06:45.190
6 detectives handle
all the stalker cases in |.A.?

06:45.200 --> 06:46.520
And any other threat
that occurs.

06:46.540 --> 06:47.826
So a lot of what
we do is consult

06:47.840 --> 06:48.864
And assist
other departments.

06:48.870 --> 06:50.133
Ben: So playing nice
is essential.

06:50.140 --> 06:52.837
Beth wants you up to speed.
Here are the active files.

06:52.840 --> 06:54.569
We handle around
300 cases a year

06:54.580 --> 06:56.400
