ongoing.

06:56.410 --> 06:58.105
Happy reading.

06:58.110 --> 06:58.975
What's his rank?

06:58.980 --> 07:00.948
He's young, d1i,
a bit disgruntled.

07:00.950 --> 07:02.679
He doesn't seem
disgruntled.

07:02.680 --> 07:05.615
