the answers to all these questions.

07:31.910 --> 07:35.744
Just small talk.
Never mind.

07:35.750 --> 07:37.013
And chai tea.

07:37.020 --> 07:39.910
I usually drink chai tea
in the morning, but thanks.

07:39.920 --> 07:41.979
